observationText: The HTh74 clone 7 cell line is derived from an undifferentiated thyroid carcinoma from a female patient.
The STR profile of the HTh74 clone 7 cell line is unique among the panel of thyroid cancer cell lines analyzed.
The HTh74 clone 7 cell line expresses undetectable levels of the thyroid transcription factors TTF-1 and Pax-8.
